Package: classifyLLM
Type: Package
Title: Tidy LLM-Powered Classification for Columns
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Dante", family = "Sanchez", role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "you@example.com"))
Description: Classify character vectors into predefined categories using a Large Language Model (LLM)
    from OpenAI, designed to fit naturally into tidyverse pipelines (e.g., mutate()).
    Includes helpers for prompts and safe fallbacks.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/dante042/classifyLLM
